<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>진급 시험 - 경찰청 통합 진급 사이트</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>진급 시험</h1>
        </div>
        <form action="/result" method="POST">
            <div class="question">
                <h3>1. 다음 중 경찰관의 직무에 해당하지 않는 것은?</h3>
                <div class="options">
                    <div class="option">
                        <input type="radio" name="q1" value="1" required>
                        <label>범죄의 예방과 수사</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="option">
                        <input type="radio" name="q1" value="2">
                        <label>교통의 단속과 사고처리</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="option">
                        <input type="radio" name="q1" value="3">
                        <label>시설물의 관리와 운영</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="option">
                        <input type="radio" name="q1" value="4">
                        <label>경비와 요인보호</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="question">
                <h3>2. 경찰관의 직무수행 중 발생한 손해배상에 관한 법률은?</h3>
                <div class="options">
                    <div class="option">
                        <input type="radio" name="q2" value="1" required>
                        <label>국가배상법</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="option">
                        <input type="radio" name="q2" value="2">
                        <label>민법</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="option">
                        <input type="radio" name="q2" value="3">
                        <label>형법</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="option">
                        <input type="radio" name="q2" value="4">
                        <label>행정법</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="submit-button">제출하기</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 